<mixer template="gw.tmpl">
<mixertitle> Feedback on the use of <mixer var="GAP"/> </mixertitle>

<p>
  If you use the Computer Algebra System <mixer var="GAP"/> in your 
  research or teaching, please tell
  us about such use. We are interested to see how <mixer var="GAP"/> is used
  for instance in order to plan the further development of the system.
  Please write an ordinary e-mail letter to 
  <mixer person="GAP" data="email_link"/>.  
</p>
<p>
We would  appreciate if  you could give  your name,  organisation, and
your email  address and tell us  about your area of  interest and your
work using <mixer var="GAP"/>.  In particular we are interested in the
bibliographic data of papers citing <mixer var="GAP"/> (if any), which
we would like to include into  the 
<a href="/Doc/Bib/bib.html">Bibliography</a> of such papers kept by
us.
</p>
<p>
  If you think that your work may be of broader interest to other users
  of <mixer var="GAP"/> we encourage you even to send a report on it to
  the <a href="/Contacts/Forum/forum.html"><mixer var="GAP"/> Forum</a>.
</p>

</mixer>
